                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-176-18541218 t18541218-176-punishment-41"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Russell Gurney, Esq.</hi>
